question_text_en: What is the video from camera4 showing an agent drinking an object whose state is GRABED in the kitchen from 2024-04-20T18:33:00 to 2024-06-04T21:36:00?
query:
PREFIX ho: <http://www.owl-ontologies.com/VirtualHome.owl#>
            PREFIX mssn: <http://mssn.sigappfr.org/mssn/>
            PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
            PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
            PREFIX vh2kg: <http://kgrc4si.home.kg/virtualhome2kg/ontology/>
            PREFIX ex: <http://kgrc4si.home.kg/virtualhome2kg/instance/>
            PREFIX x3do: <https://www.web3d.org/specifications/X3dOntology4.0#>
            PREFIX ac: <http://kgrc4si.home.kg/virtualhome2kg/ontology/action/>
            PREFIX sosa: <http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/>
            PREFIX time: <http://www.w3.org/2006/time#>
        
                    SELECT DISTINCT ?answer WHERE {
                        { select * where {
                        ?event vh2kg:action ac:drink .
                        
                ?event vh2kg:time ?time_interval .
                ?time_interval time:hasBeginning ?begin .
                ?begin time:inXSDDateTime ?begin_time .
                ?time_interval time:hasEnd ?end .
                ?end time:inXSDDateTime ?end_time .
                FILTER("2024-04-20T18:33:00"^^xsd:dateTime <= ?begin_time && ?end_time <= "2024-06-04T21:36:00"^^xsd:dateTime)
            
                        } }
                        
                ?event vh2kg:mainObject ?object .
                ?state vh2kg:isStateOf ?object ;
                    vh2kg:state vh2kg:GRABED .
            
                        
                ?event vh2kg:place ?place .
                ?place rdfs:label "kitchen" .
                
                        
                ?vs vh2kg:isVideoSegmentOf ?event .
                ?md mssn:hasMediaSegment ?vs ;
                    sosa:madeBySensor ex:camera4_scene1 ;
                    vh2kg:video ?answer .
                
                    } limit 1

qualifiers_en.subject: agent
qualifiers_en.object: an object whose state is GRABED
qualifiers_en.question: What is the video from camera4?

question_text_en: What are the start and end frames of the scene from camera3 involving an agent that grabs an object which is a subclass of Props in the bathroom for more than or equal to 1 seconds?
query:
PREFIX ho: <http://www.owl-ontologies.com/VirtualHome.owl#>
            PREFIX mssn: <http://mssn.sigappfr.org/mssn/>
            PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
            PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
            PREFIX vh2kg: <http://kgrc4si.home.kg/virtualhome2kg/ontology/>
            PREFIX ex: <http://kgrc4si.home.kg/virtualhome2kg/instance/>
            PREFIX x3do: <https://www.web3d.org/specifications/X3dOntology4.0#>
            PREFIX ac: <http://kgrc4si.home.kg/virtualhome2kg/ontology/action/>
            PREFIX sosa: <http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/>
            PREFIX time: <http://www.w3.org/2006/time#>
        
                SELECT DISTINCT ?minFrame ?maxFrame WHERE {
                    {
                        SELECT ?vs (MIN(?num) AS ?minNum) (MAX(?num) AS ?maxNum)
                        WHERE {
                            { SELECT * WHERE {
                                ?event vh2kg:action ac:grab .
                                
                ?event vh2kg:time ?time_duration .
                ?time_duration time:numericDuration ?duration .
                FILTER(?duration >= 1)
            
                                
                ?event vh2kg:mainObject ?object .
                ?object a ?objectType .
                ?objectType rdfs:subClassOf vh2kg:Props .
            
                                
                ?event vh2kg:place ?place .
                ?place rdfs:label "bathroom" .
                
                            } }
                            ?vs vh2kg:isVideoSegmentOf ?event ;
                                mssn:hasMediaDescriptor ?frame .
                            ?md mssn:hasMediaSegment ?vs ; sosa:madeBySensor ex:camera3_scene1 .
                            ?frame vh2kg:frameNumber ?num .
                        } GROUP BY ?vs limit 1
                    }
                    ?vs mssn:hasMediaDescriptor ?minFrame .
                    ?minFrame vh2kg:frameNumber ?minNum .

                    ?vs mssn:hasMediaDescriptor ?maxFrame .
                    ?maxFrame vh2kg:frameNumber ?maxNum .
                } limit 1

qualifiers_en.subject: agent
qualifiers_en.time: more than or equal to 1 seconds
qualifiers_en.object: an object which is a subclass of Props
qualifiers_en.question: What are the start and end frames of the scene from camera3?

question_text_en: What is the video from camera3 involving an agent that walks with an object which is a subclass of Electronics at a position where the Y coordinate is less than 2.47 after 2024-06-05T05:39:00 and before 2024-06-17T15:31:00?
query:
PREFIX ho: <http://www.owl-ontologies.com/VirtualHome.owl#>
            PREFIX mssn: <http://mssn.sigappfr.org/mssn/>
            PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
            PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
            PREFIX vh2kg: <http://kgrc4si.home.kg/virtualhome2kg/ontology/>
            PREFIX ex: <http://kgrc4si.home.kg/virtualhome2kg/instance/>
            PREFIX x3do: <https://www.web3d.org/specifications/X3dOntology4.0#>
            PREFIX ac: <http://kgrc4si.home.kg/virtualhome2kg/ontology/action/>
            PREFIX sosa: <http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/>
            PREFIX time: <http://www.w3.org/2006/time#>
        
                    SELECT DISTINCT ?answer WHERE {
                        { select * where {
                        ?event vh2kg:action ac:walk .
                        
                ?event vh2kg:time ?time_interval .
                ?time_interval time:hasBeginning ?begin .
                ?begin time:inXSDDateTime ?begin_time .
                ?time_interval time:hasEnd ?end .
                ?end time:inXSDDateTime ?end_time .
                FILTER("2024-06-05T05:39:00"^^xsd:dateTime < ?begin_time && ?end_time < "2024-06-17T15:31:00"^^xsd:dateTime)
            
                        } }
                        
                ?event vh2kg:mainObject ?object .
                ?object a ?objectType .
                ?objectType rdfs:subClassOf vh2kg:Electronics .
            
                        
                    ?event vh2kg:mainObject ?object .
                    
                    ?state vh2kg:isStateOf ?object .
                    ?state vh2kg:bbox ?shape .
                    ?shape x3do:bboxCenter ?pos3d .
                    ?pos3d rdf:rest/rdf:first ?pos_y .
                    FILTER("2.47"^^xsd:double > ?pos_y)
                
                    
                        
                ?vs vh2kg:isVideoSegmentOf ?event .
                ?md mssn:hasMediaSegment ?vs ;
                    sosa:madeBySensor ex:camera3_scene1 ;
                    vh2kg:video ?answer .
                
                    } limit 1

qualifiers_en.space: at a position where the Y coordinate is less than 2.47
qualifiers_en.object: an object which is a subclass of Electronics
qualifiers_en.question: What is the video from camera3?

question_text_en: What are the start and end frames of the scene from camera4 involving an agent that switches off an object whose state is DIRTY at a position where the Z coordinate is greater than -6.63 after 2024-05-01T14:07:00 and before 2024-07-05T04:10:00?
query:
PREFIX ho: <http://www.owl-ontologies.com/VirtualHome.owl#>
            PREFIX mssn: <http://mssn.sigappfr.org/mssn/>
            PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
            PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
            PREFIX vh2kg: <http://kgrc4si.home.kg/virtualhome2kg/ontology/>
            PREFIX ex: <http://kgrc4si.home.kg/virtualhome2kg/instance/>
            PREFIX x3do: <https://www.web3d.org/specifications/X3dOntology4.0#>
            PREFIX ac: <http://kgrc4si.home.kg/virtualhome2kg/ontology/action/>
            PREFIX sosa: <http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/>
            PREFIX time: <http://www.w3.org/2006/time#>
        
                SELECT DISTINCT ?minFrame ?maxFrame WHERE {
                    {
                        SELECT ?vs (MIN(?num) AS ?minNum) (MAX(?num) AS ?maxNum)
                        WHERE {
                            { SELECT * WHERE {
                                ?event vh2kg:action ac:switchOff .
                                
                ?event vh2kg:time ?time_interval .
                ?time_interval time:hasBeginning ?begin .
                ?begin time:inXSDDateTime ?begin_time .
                ?time_interval time:hasEnd ?end .
                ?end time:inXSDDateTime ?end_time .
                FILTER("2024-05-01T14:07:00"^^xsd:dateTime < ?begin_time && ?end_time < "2024-07-05T04:10:00"^^xsd:dateTime)
            
                                
                ?event vh2kg:mainObject ?object .
                ?state vh2kg:isStateOf ?object ;
                    vh2kg:state vh2kg:DIRTY .
            
                                
                    ?event vh2kg:mainObject ?object .
                    
                    ?state vh2kg:isStateOf ?object .
                    ?state vh2kg:bbox ?shape .
                    ?shape x3do:bboxCenter ?pos3d .
                    ?pos3d rdf:rest/rdf:rest/rdf:first ?pos_z .
                    FILTER("-6.63"^^xsd:double < ?pos_z)
                
                    
                            } }
                            ?vs vh2kg:isVideoSegmentOf ?event ;
                                mssn:hasMediaDescriptor ?frame .
                            ?md mssn:hasMediaSegment ?vs ; sosa:madeBySensor ex:camera4_scene1 .
                            ?frame vh2kg:frameNumber ?num .
                        } GROUP BY ?vs limit 1
                    }
                    ?vs mssn:hasMediaDescriptor ?minFrame .
                    ?minFrame vh2kg:frameNumber ?minNum .

                    ?vs mssn:hasMediaDescriptor ?maxFrame .
                    ?maxFrame vh2kg:frameNumber ?maxNum .
                } limit 1
